<h1>Privacy Policy for Kore Circle</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> April 2026</p>

<p>
Kore Circle (“we”, “our”, “us”) is a secure internal communication platform for authorized company employees.
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use Kore Circle.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>Account Information</h3>
<ul>
<li>Name, employee ID, mobile number, email address.</li>
<li>Profile information provided by users.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Messaging and Collaboration Data</h3>
<ul>
<li>One-to-one and group messages.</li>
<li>Shared documents, media and files.</li>
<li>Group participation information.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Audio and Video Calling</h3>
<ul>
<li>Supports voice calls, video calls and meetings.</li>
<li>Call metadata such as participants, timestamps and duration may be processed to provide service functionality.</li>
<li>Calls are not recorded unless explicitly enabled by the organization.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Camera and Microphone</h3>
<ul>
<li>Camera permission is used for video calls, meetings and profile images.</li>
<li>Microphone permission is used for voice and video communication.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Contacts Access (Optional)</h3>
<ul>
<li>If enabled, contacts may be used only to help users connect with colleagues.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Notifications</h3>
<ul>
<li>Push notifications may be used for messages, incoming calls, meetings and important updates.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>
<ul>
<li>Provide messaging, calling and meeting features.</li>
<li>Authenticate and manage user accounts.</li>
<li>Maintain service reliability and security.</li>
<li>Support internal business collaboration.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
<p>
We do not sell personal information.
Information is used only for internal service functionality and is not shared with third parties except when required by law or necessary to operate the service.
</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>
We use reasonable administrative, technical and organizational safeguards to protect user information.
</p>

<h2>User Controls</h2>
<ul>
<li>Users may manage permissions from device settings.</li>
<li>Users may request correction or deletion of personal information where applicable.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Retention</h2>
<p>
Information may be retained only as necessary for business operations, legal compliance and service functionality.
</p>

<h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>
Kore Circle is intended for authorized business users and not directed to children.
</p>

<h2>Changes To This Policy</h2>
<p>
We may update this policy periodically. Updates will be posted on this page.
</p>

